@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_yclcmc(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.exp((v1 + wp.abs(v2 + 0.19)))
    v2 = wp.cos(0.01)
    tmp = tmp
    v2 = v0
    v0 = ((wp.exp(v2 + 0.12) * (v2 + 0.20 + v2 + 0.04)) * tmp)
    v0 = wp.exp(0.36)
    v2 = wp.sin((wp.abs(v0 + 0.51) - wp.exp(v0 + 0.58)))
    v2 = ((wp.cos(v2 + 0.60) - (v0 + 0.87 / v1 + 0.69)) - tmp)
    data[tid] = v0
